{
  "$comment": "Slow-rotating spine templates (weights) and cardio archetypes. Spine lifts persist; accessories rotate every 4–6 weeks (see rotation.accessoryWeeksMin/Max). Every name referenced here must exist in framework/exercise-library.json — for Home profiles the engine substitutes per framework/injury-routing.md and the equipment filter (Goblet squat ← Back squat, DB bench press ← Bench press, etc.).",
